description_0: A gray and black Peregrine Falcon with a yellow beak standing on a wooden plank. There is a wooden plank wall with light shining through the spaces of the planks, a plank is attached to the wall above the falcon's head that goes across the top of the image. The falcon's head is facing the left corner of the image, its body is turned the complete opposite way, facing toward the wall toward the top of the image.
description_1: A black and brown owl is standing on a wooden plank attached to wooden walls. The owl is looking away, its body is facing the top left corner of the image. Only the owl's back and its left claw is visible. There is light shining through the spaces of the wooden planks of the wall on the right side of the image. There is a silver pole that goes along the left side of the image.
